if I attacked you during it, you know?

520
00:38:58,090 --> 00:39:00,450
I was worried about that the whole time.

521
00:39:04,490 --> 00:39:06,660
Keep your hands off the wounds!

522
00:39:06,660 --> 00:39:09,240
They'll heal once the lull passes.

523
00:39:09,610 --> 00:39:13,130
