00:45:58,120 --> 00:46:00,110
Quite cold today, isn't it?

650
00:46:26,230 --> 00:46:27,050
Senpai?

651
00:46:30,050 --> 00:46:31,580
Senpai!

652
00:46:36,950 --> 00:46:38,020
Wait.

653
00:46:38,020 --> 00:46:40,310
Please wait, Senpai!

654
00:46:41,320 --> 00:46:43,650
Please... wait...

