00:48:13,450 --> 00:48:15,830
Yeah. You were in a coma the entire time.

662
00:48:16,150 --> 00:48:17,490
That long?

663
00:48:17,910 --> 00:48:19,060
Of course.

664
00:48:19,060 --> 00:48:21,100
You're no longer immortal.

665
00:48:21,100 --> 00:48:25,560
You were robbed of the shade beyond the horizon
that was dwelling within you all this time.

666
00:48:25,560 --> 00:48:27,250
It's a miracle you're alive.

667
00:48:27,560 --> 00:48:29,190
What the hell?

668
00:48:29,190 --> 00:48:32,260
So my immortality didn't
come from being a half-shade?

